    "Then, the flatten layer is used to flatten the image matrix to a 1D array.",
    "The Dense layer tries to find the optimal features to ensure achieving the optimal output.",
    "L1 regularization utilized to achieve sparsity.",
    "The decoder is also a sequential model that accepts the input from the encoder and then tries to reconstruct the input image in the form of one row.",
    "Then, it stacks through a dense layer and finally reshapes to construct the image."
